    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 20th level, you can assume the form of an angelic avenger. Using your action, you undergo a transformation. For 1 hour, you gain the following benefits:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Wings sprout from your back and grant you a flying speed of 60 feet.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You emanate an aura of menace in a 30-foot radius. The first time any enemy creature enters the aura or starts its turn there during a battle, the creature must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] of you for 1 minute or until it takes any damage. @action[Attack] rolls against the &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] creature have advantage.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
